Join Our Team

Oowlish, one of Latin America's rapidly expanding software development companies, is seeking experienced technology professionals to enhance our diverse and vibrant team.

As a valued member of Oowlish, you will collaborate with premier clients from the United States and Europe, contributing to pioneering digital solutions. Our commitment to creating a nurturing work environment is recognized by our certification as a Great Place to Work, where you will have opportunities for professional development, growth, and a chance to make a significant international impact.

We offer the convenience of remote work, allowing you to craft a work-life balance that suits your personal and professional needs. We're looking for candidates who are passionate about technology, proficient in English, and excited to engage in remote collaboration for a worldwide presence.

About the Team:

Our mission on the Technology team is to build simple, impactful technical solutions that empower therapists to better serve their clients.

We believe technology should enable human-to-human therapy, not replace it. By removing barriers to accessing evidence-based healthcare, we aim to make a real difference in people's lives.

If you’re passionate about using your skills to create solutions that positively impact human lives, we’d love for you to join us!

Must Have:
• Advanced English proficiency (written and verbal) with the ability to effectively communicate in a professional environment.
• Highly effective, positive, and empathetic teammate with a problem-solving mindset.
• 4+ years of professional experience in software development with a strong focus on React and Next.js .
• Excellent written communication and documentation skills.
• Eager to learn new technologies and deliver high-quality, simple, and effective software.

Nice to Have:
• Familiarity with Nest.js , TypeScript , or Postgres .

